{"word":"G2287 - θανατήφορος - thanatḗphoros - than-at-ay'-for-os - Deadly","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θανατήφορος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">thanatḗphoros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">than-at-ay'-for-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Deadly</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சாவுக்கேதுவான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"death - bringing, deadly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From (the feminine form of) <a href=\"#/G2288 - θάνατος - thánatos - than'-at-os/2288\">G2288</a> and <a href=\"#/G5342 - φέρω - phérō - fer'-o/5342\">G5342</a>; <i>death bearing</i>, that is, <i>fatal:</i> - deadly.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}